node.text:
Hi beautiful.

We are here with an invitation to join us in living by the moon, in living with Soul.

We are here to invite you to join us for the next 12 months in a journey of inner exploration, inner healing, & conscious creation.

Our Flow with the Moon Membership is home to over 1200 women from across the globe who are aware of, & deeply nurturing their magic.

They’re doing so by aligning with the cosmos, by connecting to the Moon cycles, & by bringing their Soul into their everyday.

Before we go into the details - there is something to admit.

Rooted in Astrology, this membership isn't *about* Astrology.

The focus of this membership is you.

Within you is the most beautiful, unique, & powerful spark of the divine.

This membership is aimed at holding you so deeply that you cannot help but connect with, collaborate with, lead from, this spark within.

✧ What do you get? ✧

Each month you receive your online interactive guide with an overview of the month’s energy astrologically, numerologically, & through a collective Tarot Reading.

This guide includes monthly planning & intention setting, alignment tools, & new & full moon guidance.

You also receive 1-2 powerful Soul Journeys each month.

These journeys are exclusively for the FWTM Membership & are always guided by the given Moon & Cosmic energy.

With a New and Full Moon Ritual every month, each month we hold a collaboration with a Soul Leader from across the globe.

We've held collaborations such as breathwork, tapping, wealth embodiment, sound healing & so much more.

You also get unlimited discounts on all GAHM readings!

✧ Yearly Special: ✧

By investing in a 12 month membership, you also receive over $666 in bonuses.

These bonuses include some of my personal favourite Soul Journeys, like our Soul Embodiment Session & New Moon Manifestation - as well as some of our most powerful collaborations, like Past Life Hypnosis & Breathwork.

After the recent Full Moon, there is no doubt you are feeling that incredible Soul pull growth for more depth, more expansion, more you.

We would be so honored to be a part of that journey.

The link is in our bio to find out more. ♡

node.text:
Trust in your desires.⁣
Trust in your energy.⁣
Trust in your heart.⁣
Trust in your power.⁣
Trust in Life.⁣
⁣
Trust that you don’t need to hold it all.⁣
⁣
That you don’t need to figure it all out.⁣
⁣
Trust that you are growing and healing and expanding beyond what you realise.⁣
⁣
Trust that Life is coming together.⁣
⁣
That the dots are connecting.⁣
⁣
That your intention, your desire, your energy, has been heard.⁣
⁣
Trust that in this very second, and every second to come, your intention, your energy, all of Life, is bringing to you and arranging and creating your desires in the physical realm.⁣
⁣
For each of your desires already exist energetically.⁣
⁣
They exist in your heart.⁣
They exist in the cosmos.⁣
They exist in your energy field.⁣
⁣
They are already real and alive and filled with Life.⁣
⁣
And in this moment, they are manifesting into the physical.⁣
⁣
They just are. It’s just so.⁣
⁣
You are that powerful.⁣
⁣
It can’t be any other way.⁣
⁣
You are that powerful.

node.text:
A reminder that there is an overflowing source of love, bliss, calm, gratitude within you.

A wellspring that is forever in abundance.

Available just for you.

Always waiting for you to connect, to pour fullness into your being. 

🖤🖤

node.text:
Take a moment to just be with yourself.

Ask yourself what you need.

What you desire.

Let yourself dream up your biggest possible dreams. 

Lean into what it would mean to be all that you are.

There is so much available to and for you.

Our Flow with the Moon Membership collaboration with @jennablack.official is guidance into just this.

It is tapping into your mission, legacy.

Your divine creativity and contribution.

It is a deep Soul reminder and awakening:

You are the change. You are the impact.

You are wealth embodied.

The divine in expression.

You are here to own all that you are, and with that, bring about powerful shifts in the collective.

Exclusive to the Flow with the Moon Membership, you can find out more via the link in our bio!

node.text:
Combining the two incredible forces of tarot and astrology.

Connecting in with your beautiful energy.

Getting glimpses of all that Life is guiding you into in this moment.

Getting to witness your life from the eyes of Source, Soul, God.

Having the opportunity to mirror your absolute magic.

This beautiful reading is here for you to take full advantage of the Moons energy and influence in your life.

It is a personalised, unique, and magical experience of engagement with the Lunar energies.

A journey together through the fields of your energy, through the depth of your Soul.

And through the paths of communication that the Moon is interacting with you upon.

This Full Moon energy is here for you; to guide you, to support you, to remind and awaken you, and to have you come home to yourself.

This reading is here to help you get in touch with that cosmic force that is moving through you.

For more information head to the link in our bio 🖤🌙

node.text:
AQUARIUS FULL MOON 𓁿

It is Life reminding us that we are unique on purpose, that our essence when embraced and expressed fully, is what is the greatest gift to humanity.

(swipe across for times & dates across the world)

Aquarius is often a ‘step ahead’ into the future evolution of where the collective is heading.

It is the seer of the zodiac, with visions of a future that others may not yet see.

It finds paths where others walk straight past.

The energy of this Full Moon has that same seer quality.

Under this lunation, we each have access to the gift of ‘seeing’ into future potential.

We have access to unlimited reserves of the divine, to bring forward insight, creativity, insights, and evolution.

Under this Full Moon, change is inevitable.

Aquarius on its own brings about change, with the vision of our future path igniting that change. With freedom on its mind, it encourages us to break free from the patterns, structures, identities that aren’t supporting our highest growth. All that doesn’t encourage the full expression of who we are.

The presence of Pluto guides us deeper into that change, moving into the realm of total transformation – death and rebirth.

With Pluto emphasising endings, the Sun & Moon sitting at 1° looks to new beginnings.

This Full Moon is both an ending and beginning.

It is a total surrender into transformation.

It is bright and potent illumination into what was previously unseen.

It is glimpses into potential futures and who we are at our fullest, most aligned expression.

Happy Full Moon beautiful.

If anything - take a moment to just be with yourself.

Ask yourself what you need.

What you desire.

Let yourself dream up your biggest possible dreams. 

Lean into what it would mean to be all that you are.

For a Full Moon reading, or our ritual with @jennablack.official visit the link in our bio!

Jordane 🖤

Your greatest compass within.

Your greatest guide a little whisper and intuitive hit.

It's always beautiful coming into collaboration with another that you trust.

It's always beautiful expanding your perspective with the illumination of another.

But always remember.

You know your truth better than anyone else.

You know what is right for you.

Because your truth will always feel freeing in your body.

Gone are the days where we give our power away to a special few that are ‘connected to the Divine’.

You are the Divine.

Trust yourself.
